  <title>GLib.Source.prototype.attach</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function attach(context: <link xref="GLib.MainContext">GLib.MainContext</link>): Number(guint) {
    // Gjs wrapper for g_source_attach()
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Adds a <link xref="GLib.Source"/> to a <code>context</code> so that it will be executed within
that context. Remove it by calling <link xref="GLib.Source.destroy"/>.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>context</code></title>
  <p>a <link xref="GLib.MainContext"/> (if <code>null</code>, the default context will be used)</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>Returns</code></title>
  <p>the ID (greater than 0) for the source within the
  <link xref="GLib.MainContext"/>.</p>
</item>
</terms>

